SUMMARY:Myra Albert WIGGINS Celebrating a Pacific Northwest woman pioneer i
	n early American photography
DTSTAMP:20260307T061142Z
DTSTART:20260307T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Description   Exhibition and sale of rare vintage photographs b
	y women American pioneer photographer and painter Myra Albert Wiggins \\(1
	869-1956\\) All works presented are original vintage prints\, executed in 
	platinum and gelatin silver\, and printed by the artist herself between 18
	95 and 1910.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/myra-albert-
	wiggins-celebrating-a-pacific-northwest-woman-pioneer-in-early-american-ph
	otography/18243908/2026-03-07T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Community & Civic
