	en Family Wines. Each Friday\, Heritage’s culinary team will present a bea
	utifully crafted three-course menu designed to showcase the flavors of the
	 season and paired perfectly with our hand-selected Evergreen Family wines
	. \n\nEach course highlights local ingredients and thoughtful preparation\
	, creating a seamless journey of flavor and harmony between the kitchen an
	d the cellar. The menu will remain the same throughout the season\, allowi
	ng guests to savor and revisit this distinctive pairing experience. \n\nDo
	ors open at 6:00 PM for a welcome pour\, followed by dinner service beginn
